high_descs: Turn right, move to the table opposite the chair.
Pick up the knife, that is in the sun, from the table,
Move to the potato on the table that is between a sponge and a cup.
Slice the potato on the table.
Turn left, move to the counter in front of the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn right, move to the table opposite the chair.
Pick up a slice of potato from the table.
Turn left, move to the counter in front of the sink.
Put the potato slice in the sink, rinse it, pick it back up.
Turn right, move to the table opposite the chair.
Put the potato slice on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed slice of potato on the table.

high_descs: Turn around, go across the room, turn right to go around the counter and turn left towards the table.
Pick up the knife behind the sponge on the table.
Look down at the potato on the table.
Cut the potato on the table.
Turn left, go across the room, turn left and head to the sink on the right.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn around and head back to the table.
Pick up a slice of potato on the table.
Turn left, go across the room, turn left and head to the sink on the right.
Put the slice of potato in the sink, rinse it off and pick it back up.
Turn around and head back to the table.
Put the slice of potato on the table in front of the cut potato.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean slice of potato on the table.

high_descs: Turn right and head to the round table
Pick up the knife on the table
Move backward then face the potato
Slice the potato into piece
Turn left then head to the sink
Put the knife in the sink
Turn right then head to the round table
Pick up a slice of potato
Turn left and go to the sink
Put the slice potato in the sink and rinse it
Turn right then head to the round table
Put slice potato on the table beside the knife
anns.task_desc: Put washed slice potato on the table beside the knife
